ong it is."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "A combative Pok\u00e9mon, it\u2019s ready to pick a fight with anyone. It has talons that can crush hard berries."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "They pick fights indiscriminately. They grow stronger and more powerful each time they faint or are injured."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "If it spies a strong Pok\u00e9mon, Rufflet can\u2019t resist challenging it to a battle. But if Rufflet loses, it starts bawling."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "Known as a natural-born warrior, soon after its hatching, it will challenge its parent to a fight in order to gain their acceptance."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "With its powerful legs and sturdy claws, it can crack even the hard shells of Shellder and pluck out their insides."}, {"version": "white", "text": "They will challenge anything, even strong opponents, without fear. Their frequent fights help them become stronger."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "It stands up to massive opponents, not out of courage, but out of recklessness. But that is how it gets stronger."}, {"version": "x", "text": "They crush berries with their talons. They bravely stand up to any opponent, no matter how strong it is."}, {"version": "y", "text": "They will challenge anything, even strong opponents, without fear. Their frequent fights help them become stronger."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "black", "black-2", "legends-arceus", "moon", "omega-ruby", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "white", "white-2", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["black-2-white-2", "black-white", "legends-arceus", "omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "rufflet"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "braviary"}]}